下面都是非常实用的代码或者pattern, 值得好好写:

1. decimal numbers
2. phone numbers
3. emails
4. html
5. match specific filenames
6. trimming whitespace from start to end
7. parse data from url/log

可能还有更好的写法, 循序渐进吧.

